    FAST Channel FAQ's

    WHAT IS NFL CHANNEL?

    NFL Channel is the NFL's 24/7 FREE, always on channel offering NFL content. We feature Live Game Day Coverage, NFL Game Replays, Original Shows, Emmy-Award winning series and more!

    HOW CAN I WATCH NFL CHANNEL?

    You can watch the NFL Channel on the official NFL App on your Connected TV or on any of our partner platforms: LG, Peacock, Plex, Pluto TV, Roku, Samsung, TCL, Tubi, Vizio, or Xumo.

    ARE THERE LIVE GAMES ON NFL CHANNEL?

    There are no live NFL games on NFL Channel. However, NFL Channel features live game day coverage that provides fans with real-time updates of NFL game action including scores, Next Gen Stats, highlights, and more. For live game access, please check out NFL+ offerings at NFL.com/plus.
